author: hwright
msg: Do a more thorough collection of children pending commit, which both improves
performance (we don't have to run to the working copy) and correctness (we
don't include children not being committed).
(do_item_commit): For added directories, fetch children from the new_children
(svn_client__do_commit): Populate the new_children hash for all nodes.
